     <body>
     <div type="prologue">
   <head>¶The Prologue.</head>
   <l>MAny men speke / as they in the boke rede</l>
   <l>Of the paynes of purgatorye / but fewe it drede</l>
   <l>For many a man wotteth not / what thynge it is</l>
   <l>Therfore they drede it / the lesse ywys</l>
   <l>And for some men / haue therof no knowynge</l>
   <l>Of the place of purgatorye / not vnderstandynge</l>
   <l>Therfore I wyll tell / what it is in lykenes</l>
   <l>And in what place / as the boke is wytnes</l>
   <l>And whiche soules goth thyther / and for what syn</l>
   <l>And what maner of paynes / ben therin</l>
   <l>And also what thynge / is most in certayne</l>
   <l>That myght a mannes soule / brynge out of payne.</l>
</div>
